# Hotel Reservation Cancellation Prediction — MLOps Project

End-to-end MLOps pipeline for predicting hotel booking cancellations.  
Built as part of Opemioniye's 8-week MLOps workshop.

---

## Dataset

- **Source**: [Kaggle – Hotel Reservations Classification Dataset](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/ahsan81/hotel-reservations-classification-dataset)
- **Rows**: 36,275 bookings
- **Target**: `booking_status` — `Canceled` (33%) vs `Not_Canceled` (67%)

### Key Features

| Feature | Description |
|---|---|
| `lead_time` | Days between booking and arrival |
| `avg_price_per_room` | Average nightly rate |
| `no_of_special_requests` | Number of special requests made |
| `market_segment_type` | Booking channel (Online, Offline, etc.) |
| `no_of_previous_cancellations` | Historical cancellations by guest |

